column5: I'm hoping to get out for some eye's if there around, any help would be appreciated.

I was off Port Cobourn yesterday and we got a 9lber and a big grunt in 65 feet of water SE of port Cobourn.  I have kinda given up on Maitland as there are too many " should have been here yesterday" stories.    55 feet down on spinner and worm rig, grunt came 220 back on a 3 setting with a purple Nk and worm.
